<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FlexHaus Reconnect & Thrive - Your Journey Continues!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #007BFF;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            margin-top: 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
        }
        .offer {
            background-color: #e2f0fb;
            border-left: 5px solid #007BFF;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.15em;
            color: #0056b3;
        }
        .testimonial {
            font-style: italic;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome Back to FlexHaus!</h1>
        <p>We noticed you haven't been with us for a while, and we genuinely miss seeing you thrive. At FlexHaus, we believe in your potential, and we're here to help you rekindle your fitness journey.</p>

        <div class="offer">
            <h2>Your Exclusive Reconnect Offer!</h2>
            <p>To celebrate your return, we're inviting you back with a **complimentary class of your choice!** Experience the energy, community, and expert guidance you love, on us.</p>
            <p>This is your chance to rediscover your favorite workout, try something new, and reignite your passion for health and wellness.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Why FlexHaus is Your Perfect Fit:</h2>
        <p>Whether you're looking to boost your energy, tone up, reduce stress, or simply connect with a supportive community, FlexHaus has a class designed for you. Our passionate instructors and welcoming environment make every session an empowering experience.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Expert-Led Classes:</strong> From high-intensity to restorative yoga, find your perfect match.</li>
            <li><strong>Supportive Community:</strong> Train alongside friends and make new ones who share your goals.</li>
            <li><strong>Flexible Schedule:</strong> Book classes that fit seamlessly into your life.</li>
            <li><strong>Personalized Growth:</strong> We're here to support your unique fitness journey every step of the way.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="testimonial">
            <p>"Coming back to FlexHaus was the best decision! The energy is incredible, and I instantly felt motivated again." - Emma S.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Ready to Reconnect?</h2>
        <p>Claim your complimentary class and book your spot today. It's time to feel strong, energized, and connected once more.</p>

        <a href="#booking-form" class="cta-button">Claim Your Free Class & Book Now!</a>

        <div id="booking-form" style="margin-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 30px;">
            <h2>Book Your Reconnect Class!</h2>
            <form action="#" method="POST">
                <p>
                    <label for="name">Your Name:</label><br>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required style="width: 60%; padding: 10px; margin-top: 5px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px;">
                </p>
                <p>
                    <label for="email">Your Email:</label><br>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required style="width: 60%; padding: 10px; margin-top: 5px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px;">
                </p>
                <p>
                    <label for="class-choice">Choose Your Class:</label><br>
                    <select id="class-choice" name="class-choice" required style="width: 60%; padding: 10px; margin-top: 5px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px;">
                        <option value="">-- Select a Class --</option>
                        <option value="yoga">Yoga Flow</option>
                        <option value="pilates">Pilates Core</option>
                        <option value="hiit">HIIT Blast</option>
                        <option value="zumba">Zumba Dance</option>
                        <option value="strength">Strength Training</option>
                    </select>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <label for="date">Preferred Date:</label><br>
                    <input type="date" id="date" name="date" required style="width: 60%; padding: 10px; margin-top: 5px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px;">
                </p>
                <button type="submit" class="cta-button" style="background-color: #007BFF;">Confirm & Book!</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2026 FlexHaus. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
